title: "Agentic Workflow Governance (AWG)"
abstract: "A framework for designing, gating, and pinning accountability in workflows where AI agents take action: risk-tier classification, a phase model, atomic gate primitives, machine-validatable handoff schemas, and a named-human accountability principle."
